\frametitle{Global Interpreter Lock -- continued}

        Reference counting:
        any reference to an object modifies it! (or at least its refcount)
        \begin{verbatim}
            > import sys
            > a = []
            > sys.getrefcount(a)
            2
            > b = a
            > sys.getrefcount(a)
            3
        \end{verbatim}
